# 📝 To-Do List Web App

A responsive and interactive To-Do List web application built using **HTML, CSS, and Vanilla JavaScript**.  
This app allows users to add, complete, and delete tasks in real-time, and also includes a **Dark Mode toggle** for improved accessibility and aesthetics.

---

## 🚀 Features

- ✅ Add new tasks
- ✅ Mark tasks as complete/incomplete
- ✅ Delete tasks
- 🌗 Toggle between Light Mode and Dark Mode
- 📱 Fully responsive on all devices
- ⚡ Real-time UI updates without page reload
- 💡 Built using pure Vanilla JavaScript (no frameworks)

